title: [Wind Tunnel]
description: The wind speaks with a passionate voice, the voice of the damned souls that have been borne here from the swirling storm off-shore.  Throughout the years the unnatural tempest has been known by many names.  Sailors call it the Felstorm, or simply "the Squall", and you remember a mendicant preacher once mumbling something about "...the breath!  The foul breath of Luukos..."
